# errors_to in user filters and bounce_return_body
exim -odi -bs
helo test
mail from:<abcd@x.y.z>
rcpt to:<forwarder@test.ex>
rcpt to:<forwarder2@test.ex>
data
Test message.
.
quit
****
exim -DBRB=false -odi -bs
